ActDepartment of Citizenship and Immigration Act
PrecisAuthorization for the Minister of Citizenship and Immigration to enter into a CONTRIBUTION AGREEMENT with the International Organization for Migration to deliver in-person pre-departure information and orientation sessions in various countries to various groups of immigrants and refugees who have been selected by the Government of Canada for permanent resident status. The agreement is for a term beginning on July 1, 2008 and ending on March 31, 2010.
